[[File:Mark Mylod.png|thumb|250px|Mark Mylod filming in Season 5.]]
Mark Mylod is a British film and television director and producer. His most notable early directing credits are the films ''[[wikipedia:Ali G Indahouse|Ali G Indahouse]]'', ''[[wikipedia:The Big White|The Big White]]'', ''[[wikipedia:The Big White|The Big White]]'' and ''[[wikipedia:What's Your Number?|What's Your Number?]]'', and the television shows ''[[wikipedia:Cold Feet|Cold Feet]]'', ''[[wikipedia:The Royle Family|The Royle Family]]'', and ''[[wikipedia:Bang Bang, It's Reeves and Mortimer|Bang Bang, It's Reeves and Mortimer]]''. Mylod later co-produced and directed many episodes of ''[[wikipedia:Entourage (TV Series)|Entourage]]'', ''[[wikipedia:Shameless (TV Series)|Shameless]]'' and ''[[wikipedia:Once Upon a Time (TV Series)|Once Upon a Time]]''.

On July 15, 2014, it was announced that Mylod will be directing two episodes in the [[Season 5|fifth season]], the third and fourth episodes.&lt;ref&gt;[http://winteriscoming.net/2014/07/15/directors-game-thrones-season-5-announced/]&lt;/ref&gt;
